text: Klanec is a Slovene place name that may refer to: *Klanec, Komenda, a village in the Municipality of Komenda, northern Slovenia *Klanec pri Gabrovki, a village in the Municipality of Litija, southeastern Slovenia *Klanec pri Komnu, a village in the Municipality of Komen, southwestern Slovenia *Klanec pri Kozini, a village in the Municipality of Hrpelje–Kozina, southwestern Slovenia
title: Klanec
